                    <comment><![CDATA[
                    <div style="margin: auto; padding: 10px;">
                            <div class="messages" style="padding: 15px 15px 15px 55px;background: #f2f2f2;color: #676056;">
                                <h2><b>How to use JaJuMa Dynamic Shipping Tax:</b></h2>
                                    <p>Go to <b>JaJuMa -> Dynamic Shipping Tax -> Configuration -> Tax Classes</b></p>
                                    <p style="padding-bottom: 15px;">And find the <b>"Dynamic Shipping Tax Class"</b> configuration which provides 3 options:</b></p>
                                    <ol style="padding-left: 20px;">
                                        <li style="padding-bottom: 15px;"><b>No dynamic shipping tax calculation</b><br>
                                        -> Magento default config "Tax Class for Shipping" will be used for calculating shipping tax</li>
                                        <li style="padding-bottom: 15px;"><b>Use the highest product tax</b><br>
                                        -> The highest product tax rate in cart will be used for calculating shipping tax<br><br>
                                        Examples:<br>
                                        <pre class="code">All Products in Cart have tax class = 7%
-> Shipping tax = 7%

All Products in Cart have tax class = 19%
-> Shipping tax = 19%

Some Product in Cart have 7%, some have 19%
-> Shipping tax = 19%</pre>
                                        </li>
                                        <li style="padding-bottom: 15px;"><b>Use highest amount tax</b><br>
                                        -> Tax rate applicable to highest amount in cart will be used for calculating shipping tax<br><br>
                                        Examples:<br>
                                        <pre class="code">Example 1
Cart Total 100
		Books (Tax 7%)	60 €
		CDs   (Tax 19%)	40 €
		Shipping Tax -> 7%

Example 2
Cart Total 100
		Books (Tax 7%)	40 €
		CDs   (Tax 19%)	60 €
		Shipping Tax -> 19%</pre>
                                        </li>
                                    </ol>
                        <style>
